ter of their storied rivalry.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u009d#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/ev7v55tRFp  At 38 years old, Nadal's Olympic singles career is likely over.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999996105089, \"rank\": 3.895699111363399e-10, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French honored him at the Opening Ceremony by letting himcarry the Olympic Torch down the Seine River.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5329834944968297, \"rank\": 0.8175422129215123, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 0.9999999992719495, \"rank\": 7.28093502785352e-10, \"text\": \"Olympic Torch\", \"types\": [], \"